d":408123,"uid":137627,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:01:46.000Z","msg":"只覺得白色車後面架跟太貼，懷疑司機係連登仔"},{"pid":"e4128022c6617e9dec7b8ffeba67ee2682e5f111","tid":408123,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:02:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登仔"},{"pid":"9f4572c05e6c5e12cefcdc30f6ec5040a7b80f6a","tid":408123,"uid":126690,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b14f6c885e45db46f02b43f1c6f68941918307d3","tid":408123,"uid":68842,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:13:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有斜路停車怕前車有可能溜後呀，咪預鬆少少囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n揸大車咩溜後 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁嘅斜度都溜後咁西環果啲大斜路點算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7975fd6d645062ecea5d48130a959a27d6d29da3","tid":408123,"uid":68842,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:16:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔覺有咩問題, 貼得太埋你要等前車開前D先可以比油會仲慢, 白色車而家咁可以同前車同步比油, 會仲順<br />\n而家一架車個影響可能先半秒, 多車起上黎個個貼前車, 個個都要等前車開, 就塞車lor<br />\n<br />\n結論: 樓主on9</blockquote><br />\n我同意你果個開車快啲嘅論點，但問題係當個個人都為咗要起步快啲然後個個都係車留一個車位，然後遇上呢個整路封咗一條線嘅情況，後面啲車有排都行唔到上嚟，有啲去第個路口嘅亦因爲前面塞車而過唔到燈等連鎖效應，你覺得真係冇問題？"},{"pid":"6564cb44478da08f4cbf2a32b11abbb5765e79e9","tid":408123,"uid":68842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:17:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主嘅on9搞到個post好撚尷尬</blockquote><br />\n係，我好認真咁講聲 sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f3831c1ba283e936d51ff530a2a73f5d8f8459","tid":408123,"uid":27558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:18:56.000Z","msg":"白色架車你見到有人揸緊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68dd718153315cda2e8c19397f18b4e39b953f0","tid":408123,"uid":29879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:21:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你覺得跟車太貼炒埋落去唔會塞得仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\nSorry 我錯，補充翻當時停緊燈架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n整路本身已經多車，然後仲要同前車隔勁遠咁停係到，後幾枝燈啲車又唔洗行啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你知唔知咩叫塞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e411ad7131119a0bf511888e4c0234a7c9f00fc9","tid":408123,"uid":68842,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:23:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你覺得跟車太貼炒埋落去唔會塞得仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\nSorry 我錯，補充翻當時停緊燈架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n整路本身已經多車，然後仲要同前車隔勁遠咁停係到，後幾枝燈啲車又唔洗行啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你知唔知咩叫塞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只係呢個情況咁啱係整路導致塞車，然後就有架車做左個咁嘅行為，唔代表唔整路佢就唔會留咁多位架喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e443e3b084892d2060c0328239c0a3f9f2790a","tid":408123,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:35:10.000Z","msg":"何文田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a031c5213f91a753880de821c6e9d2b27bb45f","tid":408123,"uid":973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"