:2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:05:20.000Z","msg":"就係啲推車撚又無技術又要推<br />\n之後炒撚左<br />\n咪柯拔甩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上斜又唔知人地揸棍<br />\n跟到貼一貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480d86e7496ca5a1fc47012a12c6d624c6a3b745","tid":408123,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:05:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>預留距離無問題，真正塞車既原因係亂cut線</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無錯 跟車太貼炒埋仲塞得耐"},{"pid":"69b5f26ed0aa0c00b507f1901fb185c15a2f6e87","tid":408123,"uid":68842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:07:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就係啲推車撚又無技術又要推<br />\n之後炒撚左<br />\n咪柯拔甩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上斜又唔知人地揸棍<br />\n跟到貼一貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個世界唔係非黑即白嘅，唔好隔咁遠&ne;要跟到前面貼一貼，依家個距離係正常私家車都可以插到入嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db413a91cab1c21daf2d0e326836efd724fa075e","tid":408123,"uid":55463,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:19:32.000Z","msg":"一條片就睇到樓主幾on9<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4WM3ITvGn4M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4WM3ITvGn4M&d=14%2BRiHEwK6TQmmC%2FgO6X16WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=fbe72e81\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4WM3ITvGn4M</a>"},{"pid":"f00beb1810fe2fd9e6582d4bf5a84456af156011","tid":408123,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:23:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37b6602beee91f898b167bb15f362100627aae30","tid":408123,"uid":68842,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一條片就睇到樓主幾on9<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4WM3ITvGn4M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4WM3ITvGn4M&d=14%2BRiHEwK6TQmmC%2FgO6X16WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=fbe72e81\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4WM3ITvGn4M</a></blockquote><br />\n多謝你嘅影片，入面講嘅野係啱，只係我想講圖中白車預位預得太多呢個問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係預得太多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c288a0e435f3790b0008e397b976467060b27d55","tid":408123,"uid":58604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:36:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一條片就睇到樓主幾on9<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4WM3ITvGn4M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4WM3ITvGn4M&d=14%2BRiHEwK6TQmmC%2FgO6X16WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=fbe72e81\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4WM3ITvGn4M</a></blockquote><br />\n多謝你嘅影片，入面講嘅野係啱，只係我想講圖中白車預位預得太多呢個問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係預得太多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n塞車成因唔係預得多唔多位<br />\n係太多車<br />\n<br />\n你話如果架架車都預咪仲塞<br />\n我真係屌你都費事<br />\n塞同長龍係兩回事<br />\n不過你塞個時根本唔會有機會比你留到咁多位<br />\n一定有人攝<br />\n總結樓豬戇鳩鳩"},{"pid":"d56763418ae4a7716f091e0c0aab2387856744c8","tid":408123,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:38:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你覺得跟車太貼炒埋落去唔會塞得仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n停緊燈喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13dd1fb19ac6c2a333bacc373e99a276948ba13","tid":408123,"uid":77798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:50:58.000Z","msg":"Ou仔冇撚腦"},{"pid":"1c6e2463c65dbe0e15b26deb7553f9bf3c3eaa38","tid":408123,"uid":15887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:59:48.000Z","msg":"其實張圖無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喺啲人係香港習慣左